<plot>Frank Borzage, Director chronicles the life of Frank Borzage, one of Hollywood's forgotten legends. Borzage made his name as a director just as film became a major industry. He continued to be a popular director throughout its Golden Age. Borzage worked with many well-known actors- Gable,Tracy,Dieterich,Stewart - and at all of the biggest studios of his day. Today, however,he has been all but forgotten - until now. Frank Borzage, Director endeavors to shine a light on the life of a man who made films that inspired and uplifted a generation!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?202295</url></doc>
